{"title":"龙骨","authors":["程步涛"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":7,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙骨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"程步涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秦皇汉武的赫赫功业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为中华民族留下了一条龙骨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说什么孟姜女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱什么凄凄婉婉“四季歌”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就说那城堞、垛口、烽火台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说那塞外风卷来的支支长矛、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支支箭镞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说那染红的墙基、甬道的将军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪、壮士血。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜿蜒龙骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴你醒来，伴我入梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝朝夕夕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在血管里掀动鲜红的浪波。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空有龙骨，空有龙骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屈与辱写满如云史册；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯有龙骨，唯有龙骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血与火锻冶的意志如钢如铁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今，人们都在注目龙骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要打捞一个古老的文明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修补一轮残缺的皎洁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而，毕竟是千年已逝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙骨蹉跎！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想，当战争再度袭来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我决不仅仅用骨骸用血肉筑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑城会闭塞视野。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我会出击，我会前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闭塞，永远拥抱不了世界。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战死，尸体是一堆血泥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望有人看见能想起龙骨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（插图　傅旭）（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}